<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Capriola&family=Comic+Neue:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,700;1,300;1,400;1,700&family=Instrument+Sans:ital,wght@0,400..700;1,400..700&family=Kiwi+Maru&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"> 
  <title>Home Page</title>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("./partials/_navbar.ejs") %>
  <% if (user) { %>
    <h1 class="app-header">Welcome back, <%= user.username %>!</h1>
  <% } else { %>
    <h1 class="app-header">Welcome, Dear Reader</h1>
    <div class="blurb-container">
    <div class="intro-blurb">
      <h2>Reach Your Goals</h2>
      <p>Is reading more books one of your New Years' resolutions? Stay on track with Dear Reader to log your current reads as well as keep track of the books you've read in the past.
          Be sure to also rate and review the books you've read so that other readers can get inspriation for their next reads. We can't wait to see what you read this year!
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="tbr-blurb">
      <h2>Get Ideas For Your Next Read</h2>
      <p>Not sure what to read next? Take a look at our lists of popular books curated by readers like you. Add them to your TBR (to be read) so that you can reference it next time you're at the library or bookstore.
      </p>
      <div class="login-container">
        <p>
          <a href="/auth/sign-up">Sign up</a> or
          <a href="/auth/sign-in">Sign in</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <% } %>
  <p><a href="/vip-lounge">See what everyone else is reading!</a></p>
</body>
</html>
